WEBVTT

00:00:56.000 --> 00:01:00.176
I wound up as a member of the Barcelona
Symphony Orchestra in Spain.

00:01:00.200 --> 00:01:01.416
What a great life.

00:01:01.440 --> 00:01:05.016
And you know, my parents never complained.

00:01:05.040 --> 00:01:07.016
They supported me all the way through it.

00:01:07.040 --> 00:01:08.936
It wasn't their dream.

00:01:08.960 --> 00:01:11.103
They used to tell
their neighbors and friends,

00:01:11.127 --> 00:01:14.176
"Our son, he's taking a gap decade."

00:01:14.200 --> 00:01:16.040
(Laughter)

00:01:16.880 --> 00:01:18.776
And --

00:01:18.800 --> 00:01:23.696
There was, however, one awkward
conversation about my lifestyle

00:01:23.720 --> 00:01:25.176
that I want to tell you about.

00:01:25.200 --> 00:01:27.976
I was 27, and I was home from Barcelona,

00:01:28.000 --> 00:01:30.696
and I was visiting
my parents for Christmas,